        description:
            "1. We did training on finding the parent website of software and then doing all checks like compatibility, security, reviews etc. After doing all the research then downloading it and installing it and using it. 2. We did training on how to update various devices like pc, mac, android and iOS.",
        details: "",
        link: "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1yDL8yUwKOzZy9ghMgC9jOM9tOF493aVF/edit",
        linkText: "View Guidelines",
    },
    {
        title: "Digital Security Policy",
        description:
            "1. Digital Security Policy awareness event involving participants from various organizations in Dharamsala.2. Short awareness skit video on the importance of Digital Security Policy",
        details: "",
        link: "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zGyjOsf8atJ9JlBSQsodmJQt8ET_BxxjKOWw3gIcaNA/edit",
